Package maven.websphere.plugin

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DeployMojoIface  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractExportMojo
    Super class of all the export mojos, defines the output file to be executed.
    AbstractMigrateMojo<ExportMojo extends AbstractExportMojo>
    Super class of migrate mojo's, defines migration work flow for pages,portlet, theme and urlmappings.
    AbstractMultiDeployMojo<DeployMojo extends DeployMojoIface>  
    AbstractWebsphereMojo
    Accommodate MAVEN attribute, and common method which needs MAVEN attributes
    AbstractWSAntMojo  
    AbstractXMLAccessMojo
    Super class of XMLAccess related goals, define the work follow of XMLAccess execution
    DeployEARMojo
    The deploy-ear task enables you to install a new application into a WebSphere Server or Cell.This task is a wrapper for the AdminApp.install() command of the wsadmin tool.
    DeployMultiPortletMojo
    The deploy-multi-portlet task enables you to install multiable portlets into a WebSphere Portal Server.
    DeployPortletMojo
    The deploy-portlet task enables you to install portlet into a WebSphere Portal Server.
    DeployWARMojo
    The deploy-war task enables you to install a Web Application into a WebSphere Server or Cell.This task is a wrapper for the AdminApp.install() command of the wsadmin tool.
    ExportPageMojo
    The export-page task enables you to export the WebSphere Portal Page based on UniqueName.
    ExportPortletMojo
    The export-portlet task enables you to export the WebSphere portlet(s) based on UniqueName(s).
    ExportThemeMojo
    The export-theme task enables you to export the WebSphere Theme based on Theme.
    ExportURLMappingMojo
    The export-urlmapping task enables you to export the WebSphere urlmapping based on Uniquename or label.
    ImportMojo
    The import task enables you to import a XMLAccess XML into WebSphere Portal.
    MigratePageMojo
    The migrate-page task enables you to migrate XMLAccess Page XML from source WPS server to target WPS server.
    MigratePortletMojo
    The migrate-portlet task enables you to migrate XMLAccess Portlet XML(s) from source WPS server to target WPS server.
    MigrateThemeMojo
    The migrate-theme task enables you to migrate XMLAccess theme XML from source WPS server to target WPS server.
    MigrateURLMappingMojo
    The migrate-urlmapping task enables you to migrate XMLAccess Urlmapping XML from source WPS server to target WPS server.
    WSDL2JavaMojo
    The wsdl-to-java task creates Java classes and deployment descriptor templates from a Web Services Description Language (WSDL) file.
